oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Martha White Biscuit Time - 1952-09-17
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WSM program Martha White Biscuit time, originally broadcast 1952-09-17 at 5:45 am. Personnel include Ralph Christian (announcer), Faron Young (host, performer), Chet Atkins (performer), the Musical Millers (performers), and Zeke [last name unknown] (performer). Sponsored by Martha White.
